# Project Structure
This project contains Java core training materials, organized by topic. Below is the folder structure under `src/`:
``` JavaCoreBasic/ ├── HandleException/ │ ├── Handle Exception.docx │ └── Handle Exception.pdf ├── Memory/ │ ├── Memory.docx │ └── Memory.pdf ├── OOP/ │ ├── Main.java │ ├── OOP.docx │ ├── OOP.pdf │ ├── interfaces/ │ │ └── Movable.java │ └── vehicles/ │ ├── Car.java │ ├── Motorcycle.java │ └── Vehicle.java ├── PrimitiveAndObjectDataType/ │ ├── Main.java │ ├── PrimitiveAndObjectDataType.docx │ ├── PrimitiveAndObjectDataType.java │ └── PrimitiveAndObjectDataType.pdf ├── static&final/ │ ├── static&final.docx │ └── static&final.pdf └── String/ ├── Main.java ├── String.docx └── String.pdf ```
Each topic folder contains relevant Java source files and documents (DOCX, PDF) for study and reference.
